{"tid":1784970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞手足已成condom","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T05:40:07.000Z","uid":44455,"like":78,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"ee62fd22f3bab8f2a2794f1d13204bcaee61cff7","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"嚟緊20號就係尖沙咀清真寺被警嫂射藍水事件兩個月<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ds2JAS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDs2JAS2.jpg&h=3b2f70a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我哋日日煲大件事去打國際戰線 要全世界人都知道中共係唔會尊重宗教嘅大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSS9wrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSS9wrv.jpg&h=cfcd6939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁事後呢？件事只不過發生咗兩個月 我哋已經咩表示都無<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南亞手足係咪condom？</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南亞手足係咪condom？</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南亞手足係咪condom？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係！我哋要做返啲表示畀南亞手足睇！<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊20號和你哩活動 和理非、勇武、暖氣軍師都可以參加 我哋一齊去重慶大廈瘋狂消費、瘋狂食咖哩，畀南亞手足知我哋唔會好似港共政府咁隔離佢哋 南亞手足都係我哋嘅一份子 唔會分我哋佢哋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3hxudK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3hxudK.jpg&h=8be6ba6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南亞手足都係手足 我哋對手足嘅定義<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔應該拘泥於<span style=\"color: green;\">出生地</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">種族</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">血源</span>，<span style=\"color: brown;\">膚色</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宗教</span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\">文化</span></span> 否則我哋同中共有咩分別。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要會為香港付出嘅人都係手足 只要熱愛香港就係香港人。</span><br />\n<br />\n和你哩只係同南亞手足重新connect嘅切入點 我哋唔係每逢20號先當南亞手足係手足 希望大家和你哩後都會了解吓南亞手足嘅文化 重新connect我哋嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWe Connect！<br />\n<br />\n最後最後：<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3650bdb59b1556dac2e9412b5ef5336be23fe6b1","tid":1784970,"uid":294221,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"借位一用，謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27Y0Qxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27Y0Qxo.jpg&h=f8d2ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人嘅最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n專攻BNO平權<br />\n幫手解答BNO問題<br />\n<br />\n#MagnitskyAct #BNOisBritish #WeAreBritish #RightTheWrong #SaveBritish #SOSHK<br />\n<br />\nDiscuss:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MmrtBU4xLrY6fZ06gB5JPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMmrtBU4xLrY6fZ06gB5JPQ&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=0adda10a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MmrtBU4xLrY6fZ06gB5JPQ</a>"},{"pid":"4082fa8a15068c803596e3edd8ebe0f8e287eac2","tid":1784970,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc22116e6928dcb1935223444d84437c0ab2688c","tid":1784