replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"面對極權, 只有兩條路 - 依附 vs 反抗<br />\n維吾爾族人身處淪陷左嘅地方, 因恐懼而依附都無可厚非<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人做到嘅, 就係話俾全世界人聽<br />\n極權係好可怕, 但係一定要反抗, 咁先有出路<br />\n<br />\n半年前, 都無香港人會諗住反抗"},{"pid":"2d073e35ee68edf50d1df69cc680f028dc718e29","tid":1784970,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d169dabe388a797fd9479623c956753cf8015045","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38a327216d3a9072f06dfb24626fc90177c64d4","tid":1784970,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3cc0bc4a149dca0c5c50ed7234cf5fa0ee725e","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730647dc460bc6024895dcb13b025c905d5a5d4e","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d317a0ec72179f90507603e2f5c36a718396c0","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc9e0cd345e23c789638f97325660377938f764","tid":1784970,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"(區議員請入)其實少數族裔都係票源<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780205\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780205</a><br />\n其實除左增加票源,我更加想幫佢地融入香港社會同幫佢地上流,而且有手足亦係南亞人<br />\n<br />\n我發覺少數族裔有兩個問題:<br />\n1.中文學習問題,佢地好多識講但唔識寫,睇,所以會影響佢地就業,升學,唔能夠上流,相關團體反映多年,但政府仍然唔多理,支援不足<br />\n2.工作問題,佢地好多係基層,從事勞力工作,唔能夠上流,原因之一就係第1點<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議:<br />\n1.文宣方面:如果我地能夠擔保香港有真普選後,就能大幅改善以上2點,令佢地改善生活,我相信可以connect唔少南亞人,令佢地變黃絲<br />\n2.義務中文/廣東話教學:包括學生和成年人,等佢地可以便宜/免費學習中文(廣東華應該識?),幫助融入華人社會,從而改善學業,工作,可以搵相關組織協助(融樂會?)<br />\n3.多接觸佢地:理解佢地需要,難處,但要小心,要有防人之心,唔好單拖去,因為唔係全部係好人<br />\n4.youtube:搜尋少數族裔就有相關影片"},{"pid":"fc914d044751341867af911e988f7e057a8b6fd6","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a38a327216d3a9072f06dfb24626fc90177c64d4","tid":1784970,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"十連唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af105a27468bca2fa12545c24ba9f6b9af2e5a6","tid":1784970,"uid":44199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"多謝UST南亞巴介紹, 上星期已經同朋友去重慶懲罰完咖哩鋪, 之後會再介紹朋友嚟一齊懲罰"},{"pid":"5bd8bfb8bbb4bb800673c1766faf57d24aa770bc","tid":1784970,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af105a27468bca2fa12545c24ba9f6b9af2e5a6","tid":1784970,"uid":44199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"多謝UST南亞巴介紹, 上星期已經同朋友去重慶懲罰完咖哩鋪, 之後會再介紹朋友嚟一齊懲罰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05336acc2bfb731432db635de09dcf9954a0c51","tid":1784970,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a20dfbfa64d31fe8301b1b7a1de4f4d0874896","tid":1784970,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45539bd86052c9b24d83742506e760a